                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Paris"
                    },
                    "body": "not saying it wouldn't be advisable nor doable, but: if it's already in a shmem region, why not just use that already?\r\n\r\n(and I guess it's kind of implementing:\u00a0https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-4852)",
